stories.text:
Hello HN community,
The AI code translation is becoming a thing these days. Businesses are launching some sort of program to translate code to another programming language and also plain english. OpenAI is the main force that facilitated this mechanism.
Do you think AI will positively impact the learning curve of developers with this? If not, what do you think the problems will be?
stories.title: Ask HN: How do you see the impact of AI code translators?
